title: LilGuy_Respite
---
// Change Luna’s expression back to neutral 
<<show SceneSampleEvents Luna neutral>>
//////////////// Change Lil Guy’s expression back to neutral
His electric eyes wander, and become mesmerized by the sky's dusky colors.
Nubs: Today is the best day ever.
<<declare $lilday = 0>>
<<jump LilGuy_Day>>
===

title: LilGuy_Day
---
-> What are your days usually like? <<once>>
    <<set $lilday += 1>>
    Nubs: Undergoing 20-30 tests a day, with constant pokings and samplings of my DNA code. Then I get squeezed back into a capsule that's smaller than the pod you freed me from. 
    ///////////////// Change Lil Guy’s expression to worried
    Nubs: It was kind of hard to breathe in there, now that I think about it.
    Luna: That's…so cruel. Isn't that like, a violation of your rights and against federal law?
    ///////////////////// Change Lil Guy’s expression to loading
    Nubs: Title XVI, Section 23, Clause 8: It is not considered cruelty if the organism was not constructed with a bladder.
    ///////////////////// Change Lil Guy’s expression to neutral
    Nubs: I don't have one. So I guess there really is no logical reason for me to leave my capsule, after all.
    Luna: I…don't think that's the point.
    <<jump LilGuy_Day>>
-> Why? What made today so great? <<once>>
    <<set $lilday += 1>>
    Nubs: Meeting you. And getting to see how humans live.
    // If player’s $badend score is >= 5, then show this line of text and expression below:
    <<if $badend >= 5>>
        /////////////Change Lil Guy’s expression to angry
        Nubs: Even if you were inhospitable at times…
        ///////////////Change Lil Guy’s expression to neutral
    <<else>>
    // If player’s $badend score is <=4, then continue with the text below:
        Nubs: You have a good life.
        Luna: Don't bullshit me.
        Luna: There's nothing “good” about my life at all! Especially with the cards I've been dealt with.
        Nubs: Sure it is. You have all the time in the world to define how you want to spend your life. You can go anywhere you want, and know every street that runs through this city by heart.
        Nubs: And you're responsible, too—because you promised to take me back to my master once you were done with this delivery!
        Luna: …
        Nubs: You don't have to be poked and stuffed into a capsule, only to wait for the same thing to happen to you the next day. At least you have a purpose…
    <<endif>>
// When the two questions above have been played through, reveal this choice:
<<if $lilday == 2>>
    -> What is your purpose?
        Luna: So what is your purpose? Why were YOU created?
        Luna: And don't give me that firewall crap.
        Nubs: But, I really can't access those files…
        Luna: Then what do YOU want your purpose to be?
        Nubs: …!
        Luna: Okay, so you can't access it. So what? What do YOU want to do?
        Nubs seems stumped. Nothing in his database is able to retrieve a clear answer.
        Luna: I know I'm supposed to drop you off at your master's, but…it doesn't seem like you even want to go back to pokes.
        Luna: You… deserve to live....
        Nubs: Luna…
        Luna: (Why am I even saying this? It's like I'm trying to give myself a pep talk…)
        ///////////////// Set Luna and Lil Guy’s expressions to surprised
        ///////////////// Is it possible to stop the current music track so that there’s complete silence? IDK 
        ???: You deserve JAIL TIME.
<<endif>>
<<jump MaxxIntro>>
===


title: MaxxIntro
---
// Play JunkYard music track
<<play SceneSampleEvents junkyard>>
/////////////// Slide Maxx sprite with neutral expression in from the right
???: Straight to jail.
// ///////////// Set Luna’s pose to annoyedCrossed-Arms
An augmented man with the shiniest jaw and motorcycle rolls up next to me. I press my weight deeper into my motorbike, ready to bounce at any moment. 
Luna: Who the hell are you?
//////////////// Set Maxx’s expression to intrigued
Maxx: The one true ascended adonis of AGENTS, Maxx.
Nubs: That's the guy who named me T.A.B!
Luna: …Makes sense.
Maxx: Lanklets refer to me as their Chief Product Officer, but our elevated CEO prefers the new-age term “Disciple” for his executive C-suite. 
///////////////// Set Maxx’s expression to neutral
Maxx: But I digress. I finally found you after combing through hours of traffic footage from AGENTS security cameras.
Maxx: You've been driving around town with company property. If you're a smart girl, you'll hand that pillbug over and continue with your extremely jester life.
//////////////// Set Nub’s expression and pose to worried
Nubs: …

-> Over your gigachad body.
    <<set $goodend += 1>>
    /////////////// Set Maxx’s expression to intrigued
    Maxx: Flame me all you want, but everyone wishes they had my body and brain chemistry. 
    Maxx: My jaw is cut from diamonds sourced in Area 27. No amount of mewing and semaglutides could ever get you to this level.
-> And what do I get in return for handing him over?
    <<set $badend += 1>>
    ///////////////// Set Maxx’s expression to intrigued
    Maxx: Good strategy! I admire your business mindset. 
    Maxx: But the only ROI you'll get is a life behind bars for stealing AGENTS property!
-> And if I don't?
    Maxx: A life behind bars for stealing AGENTS property!

Nubs: …
<<jump MaxxThreat>>
===


title: MaxxThreat
---
Maxx: Don't act innocent, little pillbug. I overheard your non-compliant drivel with the girl. 
Maxx: You, having a life of your own?
Maxx: Once I take you back, you'll be torn apart to build Prototype 185! Though given your recent acts of sacrilege, I doubt we'll keep any of your existing parts…
Maxx: As for you.
His eyes and glass jaw glow as his system scans me and my motorbike over.
Maxx: A fake license plate, multiple accounts of going over Frisscity speed limits, and stealing intellectual property from an AGENTS lab.
Luna: (He seems to be confusing me with the person who stole Nubs from the lab.)
Maxx: I'm recording your facial data as we speak. Not only will we deactivate your SL0P account, but we'll process a warrant for your arrest and assign a century's worth of debt to your bank account. 
Luna: (I'm already swimming in debt! I can't afford any more…)
Maxx: Buuuuut if you let the pillbug go now, I GUESS I'll let you and your busted bike continue to use the SL0P app. 
Maxx: And, as an add-on, I'll drop the debt charges. Because I'm such a forgiving, ascended god.
/////////////////// Set Nub’s expression and pose to worried
Nubs: …
He's shriveling up in fear at the fate that awaits him back at AGENTS headquarters.
Maxx: So what'll it be, little lady?
Luna: (This might be my last chance to bargain…)
<<jump MaxxChoices>>
===


title: MaxxChoices
---
-> Take the deal.
    <<jump BadEnding1>>
-> Don't take the deal. 
    <<set $goodend += 1>>
    Luna: (Do it scared. Even if it fucks me over.)
    Luna: No deal. I'm keeping this guy. 
    /////////////// Set Maxx’s expression to angry
    Maxx: WHAT? Are you stupid!?
    //////////////// Set Lil Guy’s expression to surprised
    Nubs: L-Luna! But why—? Ah!
    I scoop him up and finally put the pedal to the metal. It was time to haul ass back to Root Town.
    // Motorcycle SFX sound
    <<sfx SceneSampleEvents tires>>
    Luna: If you want him, then you're gonna have to get him!
-> Tell him you're not the person he's looking for. <<once>>
    <<set $badend += 1>>
    Luna: Someone gave me this task. That's the real perp you're after. 
    Maxx: Doesn't matter. You still unlocked AGENTS-sanctioned property and that's against SL0P app policy.
    Maxx: And thanks for the tip! I'll make sure to lock you BOTH up!
    Luna: (That didn't work.)
    Nubs: Luna…
    <<jump MaxxChoices>>
-> Flirt and distract him before you make a run for it. 
    ////////////// Set Maxx’s expression to intrigued
    Maxx: Thanks, but you're not my type. I know Asian girls can't get enough of me, but they confuse me with white mediocrity.
    Maxx: Sports, beer, and women are what separate me from the average man who is ladaring. Dating would keep me from being my true, elevated self. 
    Maxx: And there's no ROI in love. 
    /////////////// Set Maxx’s expression to neutral
    Maxx: …
    /////////////// Set Maxx’s expression to angry
    Maxx: Tch!
    The guy was so into himself, making it easy for me to escape and leave him in the dust.
    I was already hauling my ass back to Root Town.

///////////// Set Maxx’s expression to angry
Maxx: Ugh. Didn't think I'd need to use this.
<<fadeOut SceneSampleEvents>>
// Stop Junk Yard music track
<<stop SceneSampleEvents junkyard>>
////////////// SFX beep
<<jump LilGuyBrainwashed>>
===


title: BadEnding1
---
//////////////// Set Luna’s pose to crossed arms with neutral expression 
Luna: (The stakes are too high. I don't want to owe anyone anything. Not anymore.)
Luna: Fine.  
Nubs: L-Luna!
I hand over Nubs without any regrets. He's just the 184th prototype, after all.
///////////////// Set Maxx’s expression to intrigued 
Maxx: Smart girl. I knew you'd make the right choice.
Nubs: N-No…!
Maxx: To the scrapyard, pillbug!
////////////////// SFX beeping
