We make it safely into the outskirts of Root Town. I park on the side of the road, and we watch Frisscity's lights glitter from the other side of the bridge. 
Nubs: There's something I don't understand, though.
Luna: What is it?
Nubs: Why did you decide to take me across The Bridge? To keep me?
