title: BadEnding2
---
Luna: You're worth a lot, so it was better to keep you close.
//////////////// Set Lil Guy as worried
Nubs: Oh…
Luna: But when Maxx said how precious you were, I thought about ransom for a hot sec. But I did the math, and it wasn't worth the trouble you've been. 
I was clearly lying out of my ass, but the little guy had been brainwashed during the whole thing. What was one more harmless little lie?
Nubs: R-Right, of course. That makes sense…
I hear dismay in the experiment's voice.
///////////////////// Set Luna’s pose to arms behind back and expression to annoyed 
Luna: I still need to drop you off too, if I want to get paid. A job's a job, and I gotta finish it.
Luna: Even if today's been a huge pain in the ass….
Luna: (And how much I hate Frisscity.)
<<fadeOut SceneSampleEvents>>
<<wait 2>>
// I imagine just the dialogue box, with no sprites appearing
I drive off into Root Town to complete the delivery. The SL0P app tells me to drop off the experiment near Val's corner store, which seems suss at first…
But I don't care. It's not worth my time to think about it right now.
I'm just trying to survive.
//////////////////////// Show a screen with THE END text, and an option to Load Game or Return to Title Screen
