I park my motorbike on the curb with Nubs on my shoulder. A few jumps through some overgrown weed patches, and I'm finally at the doorstep of the abandoned warehouse I call home.
/////////////// Slide Lil Guy sprite in from right, with the neutral-with-ears pose and neutral expression
Nubs: What is this place made of?
I hear him over my shoulder. He feels a little heavier, but I don't think too much about it. The weight of tonight has taken a toll on me.
Luna: A few train cars we cobbled together after Frisscity closed the train station nearby. They said there was “too much riffraff from this side of town.” Or whatever shit excuse that means. 
///////////// Set Lil Guy’s expression to worried
Nubs: …
Luna: (Here goes nothing…)
I take a deep breath and step inside.
Luna: Yo, I'm back.
///////////// Slide Kaya in from right with a neutral expression
Kaya: Hey, welcome—
///////////// Set Kaya’s expression to surprised
Kaya: W-What is that?!
Luna: Yeah, so his name's Nubs and he's a cyberpet.
////////////// Set Lil Guy’s expression to angry 
