Kaya: How are you gonna pay for this thing, anyway? You're already waaaaay behind on rent.
/////////////// Set Luna’s expression to annoyed 
Luna: Thanks for the reminder…
Kaya: That thing's gonna take up half of your room anyway. You'll need a crate for that thing, it's so big.
Luna: Big…?
/////////////// Set Luna’s expression to surprised
I turn around and finally take a look at just how massive Nubs has grown. 
He's grown into a full chonker.
Luna: W-What the hell!? He didn't look like that just a few minutes ago, I swear!
Kaya: SEE? We can't trust him. He's gonna grow, and shed, and leave molts everywhere. Can't have that in my witch's brew. 
Nubs wriggles off my shoulder and onto the floor.
//////////////// Set Nat’s expression to cute aggression
Nat: What a good chonky boy. I say yes to keeping him! Now lemme at him! 
Luna: 1 vote yes, 1 vote no. Called it. 
